tidy Functions tidy
&reftitle.intro;
This is the tidy extension. It currently only lists the proto definitions.
&reftitle.install;
Tidy is currently available for PHP 4.3.x and PHP 5 as a PECL extension. To use Tidy, you will need libtidy installed (available on the tidy homepage http://tidy.sf.net/) and the tidy extension from PECL http://pecl.php.net/
